-Oh. hi. Flo.

1018
00:52:37.574 --> 00:52:38.492
-Hey. Flo!
-Hi. Flo.

1019
00:52:38.575 --> 00:52:40.744
-Hey. boss.
-Hi. piglet.

1020
00:52:41.537 --> 00:52:42.746
Hi. Modo.

1021
00:52:42.829 --> 00:52:43.830
Anyways...

1022
00:52:44.540 --> 00:52:46.792
Great team win last night.

1023
00:52:46.875 --> 00:52:50.379
Socials are blowing up.
and I've got some exciting news.

1024
00:52:50.879 --> 00:52:52.548
Hey. is Jett there?

1025
00:52:52.631 --> 00:52:54.007
-Jett?
-What?

1026
00:52:54.091 --> 00:52:55.217
-Jett?
-What?

1027
00:52:55.300 --> 00:52:56.385
-Jett!
-What?

1028
00:52:56.468 --> 00:52:59.930
Oh. hi. You know that Jett promo tomorrow?

1029
00:53:00.013 --> 00:53:02.808
Well. now you're all gonna be in it.

1030
00:53:03.976 --> 00:53:06.854
Yeah. This is dope.

1031
00:53:16.530 --> 00:53:20.784
In Vineland. our roots run deep.

1032
00:53:21.577 --> 00:53:24.788
Vineland didn't just invent
the game of roarball.

1033
00:53:24.872 --> 00:53:26.707
We define it.

1034
00:53:27.374 --> 00:53:29.751
No one gets by me in the lane.

1035
00:53:29.835 --> 00:53:31.753
I don't play the long game.

1036
00:53:31.837 --> 00:53:33.589
I play the tall game.

1037
00:53:33.964 --> 00:53:35.924
Can't catch me on a fast break.

1038
00:53:37.176 --> 00:53:38.677
I make you feel weird

1039
00:53:39.178 --> 00:53:41.054
and you're not sure why.

1040
00:53:41.597 --> 00:53:43.098
And I'm the best in the game.

1041
00:53:43.182 --> 00:53:47.728
It's the end of one era
and the beginning of another.

1042
00:53:48.228 --> 00:53:50.355
It's my time now.

1043
00:53:50.439 --> 00:53:54.151
And now. it's time to pass the torch
to the new GO--

1044
00:53:55.235 --> 00:53:56.153
GOAT!

1045
00:53:59.239 --> 00:54:00.866
I'm sorry. I can't. I can't. I... This...

1046
00:54:00.949 --> 00:54:02.826
-My body is rejecting the word.
-Cut!

1047
00:54:02.910 --> 00:54:04.494
-You know what. let's just take five.
-Cut!

1048
00:54:04.578 --> 00:54:06.079
Jett. baby. what's the problem?

1049
00:54:06.163 --> 00:54:07.873
The problem is I'm the GOAT.

1050
00:54:07.956 --> 00:54:11.793
I'm not passing the torch
'cause I'm still playing.

1051
00:54:12.336 --> 00:54:15.047
It's just a promo. It's a play on words.

1052
00:54:15.130 --> 00:54:17.257
He's a goat but also wants to be the GOAT.

1053
00:54:17.341 --> 00:54:18.383
Just say the lines.

1054
00:54:18.467 --> 00:54:20.761
Are we all okay with this?

1055
00:54:20.844 --> 00:54:22.012
Now. I want to see a show of paws.

1056
00:54:22.095 --> 00:54:24.890
Raise 'em up! Who is okay with this?

1057
00:54:25.432 --> 00:54:27.142
Everybody? Okay.

1058
00:54:27.226 --> 00:54:30.103
Hey. Maximus. let's pick it up
from "they define it."

1059
00:54:30.729 --> 00:54:31.980
You got it. boss.

1060
00:54:32.981 --> 00:54:35.901
Vineland didn't just invent
the game of roarball.

1061
00:54:35.984 --> 00:54:37.486
We define it.

1062
00:54:37.569 --> 00:54:39.655
I block every shot.

1063
00:54:39.738 --> 00:54:42.199
I'm unstoppable. I think.

1064
00:54:42.282 --> 00:54:45.202
And I think there is
a power struggle happening.

1065
00:54:45.285 --> 00:54:47.454
-The end of one era...
-I'm the GOAT.

1066
00:54:47.538 --> 00:54:49.665
...and the beginning of another
that's even better.

1067
00:54:49.748 --> 00:54:50.749
It's my time--

1068
00:54:50.832 --> 00:54:51.959
-No. it's not.
-Cut!

1069
00:54:52.042 --> 00:54:53.126
Just say the line. Jett.

1070
00:54:53.210 --> 00:54:54.503
No! It's not true.

1071
00:54:54.586 --> 00:54:57.422
I don't think you understand the
difference between figurative and literal.

1072
00:54:57.506 --> 00:54:59.299
It's a double goat meaning.

1073
00:54:59.383 --> 00:55:00.926
I don't care. I'm not saying it!

1074
00:55:01.009 --> 00:55:02.427
And he's not saying it either!

1075
00:55:02.511 --> 00:55:05.639
And y'all don't even think
about saying it. Capisce?

1076
00:55:05.722 --> 00:55:08.642
Vineland didn't just invent
the game of roarball.

1077
00:55:08.725 --> 00:55:09.810
We define it.

1078
00:55:09.893 --> 00:55:12.604
I just wanna be a good dad.

1079
00:55:12.688 --> 00:55:14.982
I just wanna blow minds with sick rhymes.

1080
00:55:15.065 --> 00:55:18.777
Whoever memes my beak.
you will be hearing from my lawyer.

1081
00:55:18.861 --> 00:55:20.863
I don't even know the rules of roarball.

1082
00:55:20.946 --> 00:55:23.407
I'm the GOAT.
Always have been. always will be.

1083
00:55:23.490 --> 00:55:25.033
Not some little goat guy.

1084
00:55:25.117 --> 00:55:27.327
-It's a single goat meaning.
-Cut!

1085
00:55:27.411 --> 00:55:28.412
Cut. cut!

1086
00:55:28.495 --> 00:55:31.874
Look. since you're not gonna say the line.
why don't you just give us a little "Baa."

1087
00:55:31.957 --> 00:55:33.667
I am not saying that.

1088
00:55:33.750 --> 00:55:35.544
Why do I bother you so much?

1089
00:55:36.170 --> 00:55:38.839
You just got here. son. Who even are you?

1090
00:55:38.922 --> 00:55:41.341
I'm the one who stepped up
when you fouled out.

1091
00:55:41.425 --> 00:55:43.802
We finally won.
and you weren't even on the court.

1092
00:55:45.470 --> 00:55:46.680
Now I feel weird.

1093
00:55:46.763 --> 00:55:48.640
Is this how I make everyone feel?

1094
00:55:50.309 --> 00:55:51.643
You know what. superstar?

1095
00:55:51.727 --> 00:55:53.812
This looks like it's your promo now.

1096
00:55:53.896 --> 00:55:56.148
'Cause I'm out of here. Yeah.

1097
00:55:56.648 --> 00:55:57.816
Good luck selling tickets.

1098
00:56:01.111 --> 00:56:03.947
Jett! Wait. I'm sorry. I didn't mean to--

1099
00:56:04.031 --> 00:56:05.616
I didn't sign up for that. all right?

1100
00:56:05.699 --> 00:56:07.826
Come on. Jett. it's just a promo.

1101
00:56:07.910 --> 00:56:10.913
-It gets fans hyped for our game!
-But it's not.

1102
00:56:11.538 --> 00:56:13.123
It's how everyone treats me.

1103
00:56:13.624 --> 00:56:16.335
They all want me to pass the torch.
but I'm not done!

1104
00:56:16.418 --> 00:56:19.379
-There she is. Hey. Mom...
-I'm still here! I'm still playing!

1105
00:56:19.463 --> 00:56:21.423
We're still waiting
on that Claw. Fillmore.

1106
00:56:21.507 --> 00:56:22.883
You're better off on the bench.

1107
00:56:22.966 --> 00:56:24.051
-What?
-I love you. Jett!

1108
00:56:24.134 --> 00:56:26.762
-I just want my car. Where is my driver?
-Jett! Over here!

1109
00:56:26.845 --> 00:56:29.223
-Follow me.
-Jett Fillmore!

1110
00:56:29.306 --> 00:56:31.475
Hey. Jett. Why do you not win anymore?

1111
00:56:33.602 --> 00:56:34.770
Hey. watch it!

1112
00:56:37.940 --> 00:56:38.941
Excuse me.

1113
00:56:40.984 --> 00:56:42.236
This way.

1114
00:56:42.903 --> 00:56:44.530
This kid can move.

1115
00:56:59.962 --> 00:57:01.338
I've never broken the law before.

1116
00:57:02.047 --> 00:57:03.298
I feel so alive.

1117
00:57:03.382 --> 00:57:05.425
I actually paid for both of our rides.

1118
00:57:05.509 --> 00:57:07.052
I just wanted to see you sweat.

1119
00:57:12.641 --> 00:57:14.268
It was so messed up back there.

1120
00:57:14.351 --> 00:57:17.020
I mean. they act like
you've been losing forever!

1121
00:57:17.104 --> 00:57:20.065
I don't know what's wrong with them.
but I remember the Furball game.

1122
00:57:20.148 --> 00:57:22.860
That was amazing! You scored 70 points!

1123
00:57:22.943 --> 00:57:25.362
Well. you know why they call it
the Furball game. right?

1124
00:57:26.321 --> 00:57:29.700
Because I choked. I missed the last shot.

1125
00:57:30.367 --> 00:57:31.577
We didn't make the Claw.

1126
00:57:32.494 --> 00:57:36.456
Ever since then. Vineland's got
no love for Jett Fillmore.

1127
00:57:36.540 --> 00:57:38.083
No love for Jett Fillmore?

1128
00:57:38.917 --> 00:57:41.336
You're seriously gonna listen
to a couple of haters?

1129
00:57:41.420 --> 00:57:43.255
Where's the lie? Even I get it.

1130
00:57:43.881 --> 00:57:46.466
Next stop. Vineland City Centre.

1131
00:57:46.550 --> 00:57:47.885
Okay. Get up.

1132
00:57:47.968 --> 00:57:49.553
We're getting off right here.

1133
00:57:59.980 --> 00:58:01.940
Hey. there he is!

1134
00:58:03.108 --> 00:58:05.611
You come to pick up some extra shifts?

1135
00:58:06.653 --> 00:58:07.821
I see you got jokes.

1136
00:58:07.905 --> 00:58:09.239
Come back empty-handed?

1137
00:58:09.323 --> 00:58:12.701
You said you'd get me
Jett Fillmore's autograph.

1138
00:58:12.784 --> 00:58:14.870
Oh. my gosh. It's Jett Fillmore.

1139
00:58:14.953 --> 00:58:15.954
What's up. y'all?

1140
00:58:16.038 --> 00:58:19.416
Jett said she'd never tried the pie.
so I figured we'd pull up.

1141
00:58:21.335 --> 00:58:22.628
This is...

1142
00:58:26.465 --> 00:58:27.716
Not bad. huh?

1143
00:58:30.219 --> 00:58:32.596
Wait. is that my high school jersey?

1144
00:58:32.679 --> 00:58:35.974
Dang. y'all are some crazy stalkers.

1145
00:58:41.480 --> 00:58:43.857
What do we have here? No way.

1146
00:58:43.941 --> 00:58:45.025
Is that you?

1147
00:58:46.735 --> 00:58:48.987
Hey. you wanna meet the others?

1148
00:58:50.197 --> 00:58:55.911
My grandpappy came here from afar
to help build the Greenhouse. Yes.

1149
00:58:55.994 --> 00:58:59.081
That's little me right there in my diaper.

1150
00:58:59.164 --> 00:59:00.666
Wow.

1151
00:59:00.749 --> 00:59:02.376
We're gonna name our baby after you. Jett!

1152
00:59:02.459 --> 00:59:04.419
We're hoping she'll grow up
to be just like you.

1153
00:59:05.462 --> 00:59:06.630
Cute egg.

1154
00:59:06.713 --> 00:59:07.714
Check this out!

1155
00:59:07.798 --> 00:59:09.925
When I move my shoulders.
it looks like you're dunking.

1156
00:59:10.008 --> 00:59:11.426
Oh. yeah.

1157
00:59:12.261 --> 00:59:15.097
It definitely looks like
I am doing something.

1158
00:59:16.098 --> 00:59:17.391
Okay. so we're down by two. right?

1159
00:59:17.474 --> 00:59:19.184
I'm nauseous.

1160
00:59:19.268 --> 00:59:21.144
It's like that every time
I go to open my mouth.

1161
00:59:21.228 --> 00:59:22.604
it's like... here it comes.

1162
00:59:22.688 --> 00:59:24.523
-I can't even see straight.
-I knew it! I knew it!

1163
00:59:24.606 --> 00:59:25.858
I could tell something was off.

1164
00:59:25.941 --> 00:59:27.192
How did you get so sick?

1165
00:59:27.276 --> 00:59:30.320
Look. I'm not gonna say it's true.

1166
00:59:30.404 --> 00:59:34.825
but I will say the delivery guy
was wearing a Magma jersey.

1167
00:59:34.908 --> 00:59:36.493
Coinkydink? You decide.

1168
00:59:36.577 --> 00:59:38.996
Drumroll. please.

1169
00:59:42.416 --> 00:59:44.001
Right? Right? I told you.

1170
00:59:44.543 --> 00:59:46.962
Oh. snap. The Fillmore 1's?

1171
00:59:47.045 --> 00:59:48.338
Where did you get these?

1172
00:59:48.422 --> 00:59:51.300
A collector never reveals her secrets.

1173
00:59:51.800 --> 00:59:54.720
Just kidding. I got 'em from the store
when they came out.

1174
00:59:54.803 --> 00:59:56.597
I've been looking everywhere for these.

1175
00:59:56.680 --> 00:59:58.056
Okay. how much do you want for 'em?

1176
00:59:58.140 --> 00:59:59.266
Are you kidding me?

1177
00:59:59.349 --> 01:00:00.559
Your money's no good here.

1178
01:00:00.642 --> 01:00:03.145
They're your shoe. Just take 'em.

1179
01:00:03.228 --> 01:00:04.646
No. No.

1180
01:00:04.730 --> 01:00:07.065
Just bring back a Claw.

1181
01:00:08.025 --> 01:00:08.859
Deal.

1182
01:00:09.568 --> 01:00:10.861
Bye. Jett!

1183
01:00:10.944 --> 01:00:12.070
Later. y'all.

1184
01:00:12.154 --> 01:00:13.780
How did you know about that spot?

1185
01:00:13.864 --> 01:00:15.866
I go there for the pie.

1186
01:00:15.949 --> 01:00:18.660
It delivers every time.

1187
01:00:20.287 --> 01:00:21.496
You were the delivery boy.

1188
01:00:21.580 --> 01:00:25.042
Yeah. yeah. Was that a little too obvious?

1189
01:00:25.125 --> 01:00:26.251
Okay.

1190
01:00:27.503 --> 01:00:28.629
I mean...

1191
01:00:31.173 --> 01:00:34.384
The real reason I know the diner
is because my mom used to work there.

1192
01:00:34.843 --> 01:00:37.012
She was a huge Thorns fan.

1193
01:00:37.095 --> 01:00:38.805
-Mom.
-That's for every year.

1194
01:00:39.306 --> 01:00:41.517
Happy birthday. Will.

1195
01:00:42.351 --> 01:00:47.356
Baby. you know you could wish
for anything. so dream big.

1196
01:00:47.856 --> 01:00:50.025
You're not just going to play roarball.

1197
01:00:50.776 --> 01:00:52.778
You're gonna change the game.

1198
01:00:54.738 --> 01:00:56.114
Dream big.

1199
01:01:00.702 --> 01:01:03.288
Then. she got sick.

1200
01:01:07.668 --> 01:01:10.170
And Vineland stepped up for me.

1201
01:01:12.548 --> 01:01:17.594
Roarball was where I went
to get out of my head and just... play.

1202
01:01:18.095 --> 01:01:19.346
You know?

1203
01:01:19.429 --> 01:01:23.642
And everyone thought I was tripping when
I said I wanted to be a roarball player.

1204
01:01:24.142 --> 01:01:27.354
Everybody. Except for my mom.

1205
01:01:31.775 --> 01:01:34.486
And I want her to be right.

1206
01:01:40.075 --> 01:01:42.077
You got a lot of good folks behind you.

1207
01:01:44.454 --> 01:01:45.581
So do you.

1208
01:01:51.670 --> 01:01:53.130
See you at practice tomorrow.

1209
01:02:10.147 --> 01:02:12.774
Hey. yo. It's Mane season.

1210
01:02:12.858 --> 01:02:14.484
Oh. no. Here we go.

1211
01:02:14.568 --> 01:02:17.321
And you know. man. just at the barbershop
with P-Dogg and Boogie.

1212
01:02:17.404 --> 01:02:18.405
Let's get into it.

1213
01:02:18.488 --> 01:02:20.824
A lot of nay-sayers out there. folks.

1214
01:02:20.908 --> 01:02:23.285
been talkin' about this big game
the goat had.

1215
01:02:23.368 --> 01:02:26.288
Puttin' up a whole three points.
He's trash.

1216
01:02:26.371 --> 01:02:28.165
Thorns are trash! Thorns are trash!

1217
01:02:28.248 --> 01:02:30.125
And it ain't just the goat that's wack.

1218
01:02:30.209 --> 01:02:31.835
The whole team is cooked!

1219
01:02:31.919 --> 01:02:33.253
They trash.

1220
01:02:33.337 --> 01:02:36.048
Someone needs to shut this clown up
once and for all.

1221
01:02:36.131 --> 01:02:38.592
Hold up! Looks like we got
a special chat request.

1222
01:02:39.468 --> 01:02:42.596
It's the grandmama herself. Jett Fillmore.

1223
01:02:42.679 --> 01:02:45.891
Yo. yo. yo! Mane is on live with Jett!

1224
01:02:45.974 --> 01:02:47.184
What? Let me see that.

1225
01:02:48.852 --> 01:02:50.729
No way. bro-dents.

1226
01:02:50.812 --> 01:02:54.316
Do you know what? I'm just surprised
you even know how to use your phone

1227
01:02:54.399 --> 01:02:57.528
for anything other than reading a menu
with the flashlight.

1228
01:02:57.611 --> 01:02:59.404
I'm surprised you can talk
with teeth like that.

1229
01:02:59.488 --> 01:03:01.448
Your tongue over there
lookin' like it's in jail.

1230
01:03:01.532 --> 01:03:02.824
"Let me out. Let me out."

1231
01:03:03.951 --> 01:03:05.869
Jett's got bars.

1232
01:03:05.953 --> 01:03:08.080
I've been in the league five years.

1233
01:03:08.163 --> 01:03:09.873
already got two Claws.

1234
01:03:09.957 --> 01:03:11.250
How many Claws you got?

1235
01:03:11.333 --> 01:03:13.627
-Nada.
-Ball don't lie. Ball don't lie.

1236
01:03:13.710 --> 01:03:15.045
Well. that's about to change.

1237
01:03:15.128 --> 01:03:19.258
I don't know if you saw our last game.
but Will is shooting straight fire.

1238
01:03:19.341 --> 01:03:20.342
Archie is a beast.

1239
01:03:20.425 --> 01:03:22.177
Olivia got her confidence back.

1240
01:03:22.261 --> 01:03:23.262
Lenny's a stopper

1241
01:03:23.345 --> 01:03:24.638
-and Modo is an icon.
-Hey!

1242
01:03:24.721 --> 01:03:26.598
The Thorns are about to win
our next eight games

1243
01:03:26.682 --> 01:03:28.600
and then. yeah. we're coming for the Claw.

1244
01:03:29.935 --> 01:03:31.103
Girl. you crazy.

1245
01:03:31.186 --> 01:03:34.731
Only thing crazy is that Clydesdale hair
that you got sewn into your head.

1246
01:03:34.815 --> 01:03:36.358
Yeah. the textures don't match.

1247
01:03:36.441 --> 01:03:37.860
Drag him. Jett.

1248
01:03:39.027 --> 01:03:41.780
-Textures don't match.
-Hey. guys. don't diss the hair.

1249
01:03:41.864 --> 01:03:43.073
You know I get sensitive.

1250
01:03:43.156 --> 01:03:43.991
Jett!

1251
01:03:44.074 --> 01:03:45.492
Wait till I get off this live.

1252
01:03:45.576 --> 01:03:48.662
You know what. I hope you make a run
so I can wreck you.

1253
01:03:48.745 --> 01:03:51.248
just like I wrecked that baby goat
at the Cage.

1254
01:03:51.331 --> 01:03:54.251
Until then. keep Will and the Thorns
out your mouth.

1255
01:03:54.334 --> 01:03:55.502
These roots run deep!

1256
01:03:56.003 --> 01:03:57.129
Fillmore out.

1257
01:03:58.463 --> 01:03:59.506
These roots run deep!

1258
01:03:59.590 --> 01:04:01.425
Roots run deep! Roots run deep!

1259
01:04:01.508 --> 01:04:02.593
Roots run deep!

1260
01:04:02.676 --> 01:04:05.888
Roots run deep! Roots run deep!
Roots run deep!

1261
01:04:12.477 --> 01:04:13.896
Yeah. mama!

1262
01:04:15.898 --> 01:04:18.275
You said some pretty nice stuff about us.

1263
01:04:18.817 --> 01:04:20.152
I'm wondering why.

1264
01:04:20.235 --> 01:04:21.278
Are you feeling okay?

1265
01:04:21.361 --> 01:04:24.823
It's the first time I've been tagged
in something that didn't make me cry.

1266
01:04:25.324 --> 01:04:26.992
I don't trust it.

1267
01:04:27.075 --> 01:04:28.577
Did you mean it?

1268
01:04:29.828 --> 01:04:32.581
Look. I meant every word that I said.

1269
01:04:32.664 --> 01:04:34.166
I really do need y'all.

1270
01:04:34.249 --> 01:04:37.211
And it's time I finally acknowledged

1271
01:04:37.294 --> 01:04:40.297
that I've got some really good folks
behind me.

1272
01:04:40.839 --> 01:04:42.758
-Yeah.
-Really?

1273
01:04:42.841 --> 01:04:46.303
To show you how serious I am.
I'm ready to shake some things up.

1274
01:04:48.347 --> 01:04:52.809
I'm officially naming Dennis
the new head coach of the Thorns.

1275
01:04:54.895 --> 01:04:57.481
But I'm already head coach.

1276
01:04:57.564 --> 01:05:00.108
I know. But now. it's. like.
for real this time.

1277
01:05:00.192 --> 01:05:01.818
You're gonna be head coach. Only coach.

1278
01:05:03.320 --> 01:05:04.738
The team is yours. Dennis.

1279
01:05:05.531 --> 01:05:07.032
Yeah. man!

1280
01:05:08.242 --> 01:05:09.660
Let's go. baby. Give it up.

1281
01:05:09.743 --> 01:05:11.912
My therapist said this day
would never come.

1282
01:05:12.496 --> 01:05:13.539
Just give me a second.

1283
01:05:14.039 --> 01:05:16.333
Dennis. get it together. Get it together.

1284
01:05:16.416 --> 01:05:18.335
Get. It. Together.

1285
01:05:23.549 --> 01:05:28.554
I've been watching. learning.
waiting for this day.

1286
01:05:28.637 --> 01:05:30.138
-I'm scared.
-We like it.

1287
01:05:30.222 --> 01:05:34.810
We are going to rip the heart
out of this league

1288
01:05:34.893 --> 01:05:36.562
and make 'em look at it.

1289
01:05:36.645 --> 01:05:37.938
Nice.

1290
01:05:38.021 --> 01:05:42.818
Welcome to Dennis's world of pain.

1291
01:05:46.321 --> 01:05:49.074
Archie. you don't have to worry
about your little girls

1292
01:05:49.157 --> 01:05:50.659
growing up with violent tendencies.

1293
01:05:50.742 --> 01:05:52.327
Charge!

1294
01:05:52.411 --> 01:05:55.998
They've gone full-tilt
365-days-a-year psychopath.

1295
01:05:56.081 --> 01:05:58.667
Actually. it's 364.

1296
01:05:58.750 --> 01:06:00.294
We take Christmas off.

1297
01:06:00.377 --> 01:06:02.129
Stop thinking of yourself as an enforcer.

1298
01:06:02.212 --> 01:06:04.298
You're a protector.

1299
01:06:04.381 --> 01:06:07.217
Your teammates are like
your daughters too.

1300
01:06:07.301 --> 01:06:08.302
Protect them.

1301
01:06:08.385 --> 01:06:10.470
Hey. hands off my beautiful daughter.

1302
01:06:10.554 --> 01:06:11.638
Good looking out. Archie.

1303
01:06:11.722 --> 01:06:13.056
Wait. what did you just call me?

1304
01:06:13.974 --> 01:06:18.645
Lenny. team after team used you
for your height and threw you away.

1305
01:06:18.729 --> 01:06:20.397
So you lost your drive.

1306
01:06:20.480 --> 01:06:22.691
Ten teams in ten years. Coach.

1307
01:06:22.774 --> 01:06:25.194
Well. this team has your back.

1308
01:06:25.277 --> 01:06:27.487
So stick your neck out for them.

1309
01:06:27.571 --> 01:06:29.656
Now tear the roof off this mother!

1310
01:06:35.204 --> 01:06:36.038
Bang!

1311
01:06:36.121 --> 01:06:38.874
-Nice one. Lenny.
-That's my squad.

1312
01:06:38.957 --> 01:06:41.752
That's my squad. I kind of like that.

1313
01:06:41.835 --> 01:06:42.794
Olivia.

1314
01:06:42.878 --> 01:06:44.505
One second. I'm just...

1315
01:06:44.588 --> 01:06:46.006
-Seriously. give me your phone.
-Oh. no.

1316
01:06:46.089 --> 01:06:47.633
You are never seeing it again.

1317
01:06:49.051 --> 01:06:50.052
Another phone?

1318
01:06:50.135 --> 01:06:52.679
Where are you getting all these phones?

1319
01:06:52.763 --> 01:06:56.850
Olivia. get your head out of the phone
and into the game!

1320
01:06:59.520 --> 01:07:02.231
You were drafted number one for a reason.

1321
01:07:02.314 --> 01:07:04.942
The only thing holding you back is you.

1322
01:07:05.025 --> 01:07:07.778
You are still that bird.

1323
01:07:12.032 --> 01:07:14.117
I am that bird.

1324
01:07:14.993 --> 01:07:16.411
Will. Jett.

1325
01:07:16.495 --> 01:07:18.956
I'm gonna coach the scat out of you.

1326
01:07:19.039 --> 01:07:21.208
-Dennis. there's kids here.
-Scat! Scat! Scat!

1327
01:07:21.291 --> 01:07:25.629
Jett. remember these three words.
"Pass the ball."

1328
01:07:25.712 --> 01:07:27.965
-Like. let the ball go?
-Jett.

1329
01:07:28.048 --> 01:07:30.384
You mean share? With the others?

1330
01:07:30.467 --> 01:07:31.718
I don't think this lesson is for me.

1331
01:07:31.802 --> 01:07:33.303
-Trust your team.
-Open!

1332
01:07:33.387 --> 01:07:34.721
Jett. pass the ball.

1333
01:07:35.597 --> 01:07:37.641
-It's harder than it looks.
-I'm open.

1334
01:07:38.475 --> 01:07:39.685
-Pass it!
-What?

1335
01:07:41.520 --> 01:07:42.896
-Jett.
-I got it. I got it.

1336
01:07:42.980 --> 01:07:44.815
-Pass the ball. Jett.
-No. no. no. no.

1337
01:07:44.898 --> 01:07:48.277
Dennis. No. no. Dennis.
No. no. no. Dennis!

1338
01:07:52.781 --> 01:07:54.157
Yes! Yes!

1339
01:07:54.241 --> 01:07:57.119
Now just do that 500.000 more times.

1340
01:07:57.202 --> 01:07:58.662
You. big hairy guy.

1341
01:07:58.745 --> 01:08:00.789
Block everything that
the kid throws your way.

1342
01:08:00.873 --> 01:08:05.169
And you. that's 12 feet of grizzly.
Figure it out.

1343
01:08:06.086 --> 01:08:07.087
Blocked.

1344
01:08:08.714 --> 01:08:10.090
-Blocked.
-Dang.

1345
01:08:10.591 --> 01:08:11.592
-Hey.
-Blocked.

1346
01:08:12.885 --> 01:08:14.219
Blocked.

1347
01:08:14.303 --> 01:08:18.098
Will. you gotta find a way
to get your shot over him.

1348
01:08:18.182 --> 01:08:19.015
And Modo--

1349
01:08:19.099 --> 01:08:21.685
Wait. wait. Say it with your mind.

1350
01:08:22.352 --> 01:08:24.145
Message!

1351
01:08:24.229 --> 01:08:25.229
Yeah. yeah.

1352
01:08:26.689 --> 01:08:28.192
Received.

1353
01:08:28.274 --> 01:08:30.652
If you do all this.
you'll be more than a team.

1354
01:08:30.736 --> 01:08:33.447
You'll be a unit. Unstoppable.

1355
01:08:33.529 --> 01:08:34.615
Roots run deep!

1356
01:08:34.698 --> 01:08:37.783
"Goat Tears" is wack.
and I can't let it stand.

1357
01:08:37.868 --> 01:08:41.662
So. Will. I've prepared a little something

1358
01:08:41.747 --> 01:08:43.957
to say "thank you"
for pushing us this far.

1359
01:08:44.957 --> 01:08:46.292
That's my squad. that's my squad

1360
01:08:46.376 --> 01:08:48.712
Here you go. Ms Fillmore.
Can I get a picture?

1361
01:08:49.880 --> 01:08:52.674
Shout out to my squad
Throw me the alley-oop

1362
01:08:52.758 --> 01:08:54.051
I'm always at the top...

1363
01:08:54.134 --> 01:08:55.344
No way.

1364
01:08:55.426 --> 01:08:56.761
Nice to meet you. Theo.

1365
01:08:56.845 --> 01:08:59.264
And this is for your dad.

1366
01:09:00.349 --> 01:09:02.059
We not horsin' round with you. okay

1367
01:09:02.142 --> 01:09:04.895
Uno reverse. You like that. Modo?

1368
01:09:04.978 --> 01:09:06.188
-Give me some.
-Uno.

1369
01:09:06.270 --> 01:09:08.023
Sorry. horsey. gotta roast ya

1370
01:09:08.106 --> 01:09:09.649
Looks like Mr Pony turnin' into Mr Phoney

1371
01:09:09.733 --> 01:09:10.734
Will.

1372
01:09:10.817 --> 01:09:14.321
Lenny G the one and only
And I always got my homies

1373
01:09:14.404 --> 01:09:15.948
Slamalamadingdong!

1374
01:09:16.031 --> 01:09:18.242
That's my squad. hey
That's my squad. hey

1375
01:09:18.325 --> 01:09:19.243
Olivia.

1376
01:09:19.326 --> 01:09:20.743
I love my squad. hey

1377
01:09:20.827 --> 01:09:21.953
Yo. Lenny!

1378
01:09:23.372 --> 01:09:26.250
Shout out to my squad
Throw me the alley-oop

1379
01:09:26.332 --> 01:09:29.795
I'm always at the top
'Cause I'm taller than the hoop

1380
01:09:29.877 --> 01:09:31.087
Horns on. everybody.

1381
01:09:31.171 --> 01:09:33.423
Thorns have really found their groove.

1382
01:09:33.506 --> 01:09:36.176
And is it me. or is Modo looking
different these days?

1383
01:09:36.260 --> 01:09:38.761
Oh. yeah. He's a thirst trap. Chuck.

1384
01:09:38.845 --> 01:09:40.346
Go long for my skin.

1385
01:09:40.430 --> 01:09:41.807
Marry me. Modo.

1386
01:09:41.890 --> 01:09:43.183
No. marry me!

1387
01:09:43.767 --> 01:09:45.060
Thorns! Thorns!

1388
01:09:45.143 --> 01:09:47.770
The Thorns punch their ticket
to the Roar Four

1389
01:09:47.854 --> 01:09:49.439
and are heading to the play-offs.

1390
01:09:49.523 --> 01:09:51.608
What a turnaround. Chuck!

1391
01:09:51.692 --> 01:09:54.528
If I were Mane. I'd be shaking
in my horseshoes

1392
01:09:54.611 --> 01:09:56.822
'cause the Thorns are coming for him.

1393
01:09:56.905 --> 01:10:00.284
Looks like Mr Pony
Turnin' into Mr Phoney...

1394
01:10:00.367 --> 01:10:01.743
Do we have a deal?

1395
01:10:03.745 --> 01:10:04.746
Good.

1396
01:10:04.830 --> 01:10:08.250
Coach Dennis. how about a comment
on this team's epic turnaround?

1397
01:10:08.333 --> 01:10:09.585
How's it feel. Dennis?

1398
01:10:09.668 --> 01:10:12.462
It feels like victory!

1399
01:10:21.555 --> 01:10:22.556
Yay!

1400
01:10:22.639 --> 01:10:26.435
Okay. didn't know an ostrich
could get that fly. I see you. Olivia.

1401
01:10:26.518 --> 01:10:30.981
You know what they say.
birds of a feather look fly together.

1402
01:10:32.107 --> 01:10:34.193
Archie's a whole vibe.

1403
01:10:34.735 --> 01:10:38.322
Yeah. buddy. I look good and I play good.

1404
01:10:39.698 --> 01:10:43.702
If Modo were any more of a snack.
he'd eat himself.

1405
01:10:43.785 --> 01:10:45.662
Love it. Love it.

1406
01:10:47.664 --> 01:10:49.124
I'll be right back.

1407
01:10:50.209 --> 01:10:52.085
Anyone know where Jett is?

1408
01:10:52.169 --> 01:10:53.212
I'll go get her.

1409
01:10:53.837 --> 01:10:57.966
From the Vineland Thorns. at guard.
Jett Fillmore!

1410
01:10:58.050 --> 01:10:59.593
I sold this team.

1411
01:11:00.260 --> 01:11:03.805
The new Thorns are relocating
to Sunken City.

1412
01:11:03.889 --> 01:11:06.850
I'm sorry. what? You're joking.

1413
01:11:06.934 --> 01:11:10.270
I never joke about money. honey.

1414
01:11:10.354 --> 01:11:13.148
I brought Will onto this team
to put butts in seats.

1415
01:11:13.232 --> 01:11:16.068
but I didn't expect
for you to actually win.

1416
01:11:16.151 --> 01:11:18.153
I'm selling while the getting's good.

1417
01:11:18.987 --> 01:11:20.572
What's gonna happen to the team?

1418
01:11:21.114 --> 01:11:25.536
They're all gone. sweetie. Cleaning house.

1419
01:11:25.619 --> 01:11:27.538
And as for you...

1420
01:11:29.248 --> 01:11:35.504
I made sure the new owners knew
all about your worn-out body.

1421
01:11:35.587 --> 01:11:40.551
And surprise. surprise.
they weren't about to waste money

1422
01:11:40.634 --> 01:11:43.804
on an old. broken-down player

1423
01:11:43.887 --> 01:11:47.015
who's never gonna win a Claw!

1424
01:11:48.475 --> 01:11:52.938
And tell the team to clean out
their lockers after y'all lose.

1425
01:11:53.021 --> 01:11:56.733
Enjoy your early retirement. Jett.

1426
01:11:57.359 --> 01:11:59.903
Hey. good luck out there tonight.

1427
01:12:03.991 --> 01:12:06.118
Jett. Flo sold the Thorns?

1428
01:12:06.201 --> 01:12:08.495
-You listening in on my conversations now?
-We need to go tell the team.

1429
01:12:08.579 --> 01:12:10.205
No. we'll tell them after the game.

1430
01:12:10.289 --> 01:12:12.124
If we tell them now. they'll fall apart.

1431
01:12:12.207 --> 01:12:13.292
This affects all of us.

1432
01:12:13.375 --> 01:12:15.836
Whatever's coming.
we got to face it together.

1433
01:12:15.919 --> 01:12:18.213
Who's team captain here? You or me?

1434
01:12:18.297 --> 01:12:20.507
-Jett.
-After the game.

1435
01:12:24.136 --> 01:12:26.138
Welcome to the Cryosphere.

1436
01:12:26.221 --> 01:12:30.767
Tonight. the Shivers face the Thorns
in the semi-final game.

1437
01:12:30.851 --> 01:12:33.270
The winner marches
triumphantly to the finals

1438
01:12:33.353 --> 01:12:36.899
to battle for a championship
and eternal glory.

1439
01:12:36.982 --> 01:12:40.277
The loser?
Banished to the cold void of history.

1440
01:12:40.360 --> 01:12:41.945
This is not just a game.

1441
01:12:42.029 --> 01:12:43.822
It is a reckoning.

1442
01:12:50.913 --> 01:12:53.916
Lenny. are you trying to get traded?

1443
01:12:53.999 --> 01:12:55.292
Hey. hey. Jett. you good?

1444
01:12:55.375 --> 01:12:56.793
Focus on the game.

1445
01:12:57.294 --> 01:12:59.254
Don't worry about it.
We'll get the next one.

1446
01:13:00.672 --> 01:13:01.673
Olivia.

1447
01:13:02.466 --> 01:13:03.383
One more pass.

1448
01:13:03.467 --> 01:13:05.552
Next time you think about shooting. don't.

1449
01:13:06.345 --> 01:13:08.055
I'm sorry. Jett.

1450
01:13:08.138 --> 01:13:09.723
And that's the half.

1451
01:13:11.767 --> 01:13:12.768
Maybe we should tell them now.

1452
01:13:12.851 --> 01:13:14.520
After the game.

1453
01:13:23.237 --> 01:13:24.696
Don't hurt yourself. grandma.

1454
01:13:24.780 --> 01:13:27.241
Catch! Yeah!

1455
01:13:29.243 --> 01:13:31.119
The icebreaker!

1456
01:13:31.203 --> 01:13:33.330
And Harris is slow to get up.

1457
01:13:33.413 --> 01:13:35.040
So much for that Claw.

1458
01:13:35.123 --> 01:13:35.958
Thanks.

1459
01:13:36.041 --> 01:13:38.502
Thorns are down by 15
late in the fourth quarter.

1460
01:13:38.585 --> 01:13:41.421
It is not looking good
for their play-off hopes.

1461
01:13:42.089 --> 01:13:44.132
What is going on out there?

1462
01:13:44.216 --> 01:13:46.677
Jett. tell them. They need to know.

1463
01:13:46.760 --> 01:13:47.803
What did I say?

1464
01:13:47.886 --> 01:13:50.138
Flo sold the team to Sunken City.

1465
01:13:50.222 --> 01:13:52.391
None of us are going with it.

1466
01:13:52.474 --> 01:13:53.809
Can she even do that?
Is that even allowed?

1467
01:13:53.892 --> 01:13:55.644
We were playing well.
We just started gelling.

1468
01:13:55.727 --> 01:13:57.896
-She sold our team?
-There are rules.

1469
01:13:57.980 --> 01:14:00.274
-I thought you had a championship.
-Could have been a legend. instead...

1470
01:14:00.357 --> 01:14:05.279
Broken-down player
who's never gonna win a Claw!

1471
01:14:05.362 --> 01:14:07.322
Just get me the ball.

1472
01:14:07.406 --> 01:14:09.241
I'm not going out like this.

1473
01:14:09.324 --> 01:14:11.285
Don't you mean "we"?

1474
01:14:11.368 --> 01:14:13.453
I know that look.

1475
01:14:17.875 --> 01:14:19.626
What do you think you're doing?

1476
01:14:20.335 --> 01:14:22.129
That's two. Thorns down by ten.

1477
01:14:22.212 --> 01:14:23.422
Come on.

1478
01:14:23.922 --> 01:14:25.048
We got to D up.

1479
01:14:26.091 --> 01:14:27.634
Somebody get a body on her.

1480
01:14:28.760 --> 01:14:29.845
Come on.

1481
01:14:31.138 --> 01:14:33.932
-Pass!
-We've seen this before. Rusty.

1482
01:14:34.016 --> 01:14:36.977
It's the Jett Fillmore show now.

1483
01:14:37.060 --> 01:14:38.979
Jett with the pull-up. Thorns down eight.

1484
01:14:42.024 --> 01:14:43.150
Heads up!

1485
01:14:45.152 --> 01:14:46.945
That deficit is cut to five.

1486
01:14:48.655 --> 01:14:50.157
It's a one-point game.

1487
01:14:50.240 --> 01:14:53.202
-Ball! Now!
-It all comes down to this!

1488
01:14:53.285 --> 01:14:55.037
-Archie!
-Give me that. small.

1489
01:14:55.120 --> 01:14:56.371
Boost me!

1490
01:14:58.540 --> 01:15:00.918
Will Harris for the win!

1491
01:15:04.671 --> 01:15:05.756
Yeah!

1492
01:15:05.839 --> 01:15:08.759
Thorns win! Thorns win!

1493
01:15:08.842 --> 01:15:10.969
They're headed to the Claw!

1494
01:15:15.974 --> 01:15:17.643
So it looks like we're going to the...

1495
01:15:19.895 --> 01:15:20.979
to the finals.

1496
01:15:24.316 --> 01:15:27.569
Wow. I'm done. Team's sold anyway.

1497
01:15:27.653 --> 01:15:29.655
-Come on. girls.
-I'm not sticking around for this.

1498
01:15:29.738 --> 01:15:30.948
Modo as well.

1499
01:15:35.661 --> 01:15:37.746
You used to be my favourite player.

1500
01:15:38.622 --> 01:15:39.748
Until today.

1501
01:15:40.999 --> 01:15:42.793
What a turn of events.

1502
01:15:42.876 --> 01:15:47.506
The Thorns have a shot at the Claw.
but Vineland has lost their team.

1503
01:15:47.589 --> 01:15:49.925
I'll tell you. Rusty.
I would hate to be a Thorns fan

1504
01:15:50.008 --> 01:15:51.218
right about now.

1505
01:17:06.502 --> 01:17:08.295
Come on. Let's go!

1506
01:17:09.505 --> 01:17:10.339
I got it!

1507
01:17:11.089 --> 01:17:12.090
Yeah!

1508
01:17:12.591 --> 01:17:13.884
Smalls can ball.

1509
01:17:14.968 --> 01:17:16.053
Yeah!

1510
01:17:17.638 --> 01:17:18.764
-Wait. is that...
-No way.

1511
01:17:18.847 --> 01:17:19.932
-Hey. Will.
-Hey. Will.

1512
01:17:20.766 --> 01:17:22.559
Goat? Ball.

1513
01:17:24.520 --> 01:17:26.855
Yo. shouldn't you be getting ready
to face the Magma?

1514
01:17:26.939 --> 01:17:28.649
Did you not watch the game?

1515
01:17:28.732 --> 01:17:30.859
I don't think Jett
wants to play with us anymore.

1516
01:17:31.401 --> 01:17:33.111
I'm willing to bet she does.

1517
01:17:34.613 --> 01:17:36.907
Hey. Can we talk?

1518
01:17:36.990 --> 01:17:37.991
I'm busy.

1519
01:17:38.075 --> 01:17:39.201
-No. he's not.
-Come on. come on.

1520
01:17:39.284 --> 01:17:41.954
-Give... Give me the ball.
-No. Not happening. My ball now.

1521
01:17:43.956 --> 01:17:47.459
I came to say I'm-I'm sorry.

1522
01:17:47.543 --> 01:17:49.753
Okay. Well. you did it. So...

1523
01:17:49.837 --> 01:17:52.756
Please. just hear me out.

1524
01:17:57.636 --> 01:17:59.596
I want to win.

1525
01:18:00.597 --> 01:18:02.015
I want to hold up that Claw

1526
01:18:02.099 --> 01:18:05.644
and feel what it's like
to be one of the greats.

1527
01:18:06.603 --> 01:18:09.648
When Flo said all that stuff
about me being washed-up.

1528
01:18:10.148 --> 01:18:11.525
it just... it-it...

1529
01:18:12.359 --> 01:18:13.652
it just got in my head.

1530
01:18:14.278 --> 01:18:18.407
And I couldn't let it go
because deep down. deep. deep down.

1531
01:18:19.241 --> 01:18:20.951
I'm scared she's right.

1532
01:18:21.577 --> 01:18:23.036
And I just panicked.

1533
01:18:23.912 --> 01:18:25.873
And I did you all so dirty.

1534
01:18:25.956 --> 01:18:29.459
And I'm so sorry.

1535
01:18:33.130 --> 01:18:34.923
You know. I really thought that

1536
01:18:35.007 --> 01:18:37.593
if I was holding a Claw
at the end of the day.

1537
01:18:37.676 --> 01:18:39.803
it wouldn't matter how I got it.

1538
01:18:39.887 --> 01:18:41.471
But when you think about it.

1539
01:18:41.555 --> 01:18:43.765
that's kind of all that matters.

1540
01:18:45.225 --> 01:18:48.353
That was a really good apology.

1541
01:18:48.437 --> 01:18:52.524
But you know.
you still owe the diner a Claw.

1542
01:18:53.525 --> 01:18:55.777
It's gonna be hard to win without a team.

1543
01:18:55.861 --> 01:18:57.863
I might know a few folks.

1544
01:18:58.989 --> 01:19:00.741
-Dad.
-Daddy clown!

1545
01:19:00.824 --> 01:19:02.326
Oh. thank God.

1546
01:19:02.409 --> 01:19:03.785
-These girls are crazy.
-Daddy. Daddy.

1547
01:19:03.869 --> 01:19:06.538
Get me out of here. Quick. start the car.

1548
01:19:11.126 --> 01:19:12.461
Yo.

1549
01:19:15.047 --> 01:19:15.881
Sup. Olivia?

1550
01:19:15.964 --> 01:19:18.175
Come on. We've got a game to win.

1551
01:19:18.258 --> 01:19:19.259
Yes!

1552
01:19:40.322 --> 01:19:42.991
This is what dreams are made of. Rusty.

1553
01:19:43.075 --> 01:19:44.826
Teams become champions.

1554
01:19:44.910 --> 01:19:46.954
Players become legends.

1555
01:19:50.082 --> 01:19:51.083
Let's go!

1556
01:19:55.921 --> 01:19:58.298
-Go. Thorns!
-This is the best day of my life.

1557
01:19:58.382 --> 01:19:59.925
I can feel myself getting invested.

1558
01:20:00.008 --> 01:20:03.178
Who cares? I'm here for it.
Break my heart. kiddo!

1559
01:20:03.262 --> 01:20:05.180
Come on. Will. Let's go!

1560
01:20:05.264 --> 01:20:06.849
Go. Thorns! Go. Thorns!

1561
01:20:06.932 --> 01:20:10.018
Tonight. Jett and Mane
will finally answer the question.

1562
01:20:10.102 --> 01:20:12.271
-who is the GOAT?
-On three.

1563
01:20:12.354 --> 01:20:14.565
-One. two. three.
-Roots run deep!

1564
01:20:15.649 --> 01:20:18.068
And here we go. Chuck.

1565
01:20:19.361 --> 01:20:20.821
Unbelievable!

1566
01:20:20.904 --> 01:20:23.240
Mane Attraction gets the tip over Lenny.

1567
01:20:27.160 --> 01:20:30.831
Mane drills one home.
sending a strong message to the Thorns.

1568
01:20:33.584 --> 01:20:35.961
You're too small.

1569
01:20:37.421 --> 01:20:38.422
Come on. Will.

1570
01:20:38.505 --> 01:20:40.591
Show 'em who's too small.

1571
01:20:45.470 --> 01:20:46.388
Eyes on me.

1572
01:20:48.265 --> 01:20:49.641
Jett with the sweet pass.

1573
01:20:50.184 --> 01:20:51.018
Thorns respond.

1574
01:20:51.101 --> 01:20:52.060
Yeah!

1575
01:20:52.811 --> 01:20:56.398
As the first quarter comes to a close.
it's still anyone's game.

1576
01:20:57.441 --> 01:20:59.276
We should be frying these fools.

1577
01:20:59.359 --> 01:21:03.363
Take 'em out if you have to.
but hold on to that lead.

1578
01:21:07.034 --> 01:21:08.076
Harris on a break!

1579
01:21:08.160 --> 01:21:09.661
Nuh-uh! Not today!

1580
01:21:09.745 --> 01:21:10.913
Will. watch out!

1581
01:21:14.249 --> 01:21:15.417
Hard hit on Jett.

1582
01:21:15.501 --> 01:21:16.835
No foul call.

1583
01:21:18.295 --> 01:21:19.338
What?

1584
01:21:23.175 --> 01:21:24.635
Oh. no.

1585
01:21:28.013 --> 01:21:30.224
This injury could take you out permanently

1586
01:21:30.307 --> 01:21:32.476
if you put any more weight on this leg.

1587
01:21:34.645 --> 01:21:35.646
I'm sorry. y'all.

1588
01:21:35.729 --> 01:21:36.980
Jett.

1589
01:21:37.523 --> 01:21:39.399
I didn't mean for you to get hurt.

1590
01:21:39.483 --> 01:21:41.318
Hey. hey. It's not your fault.

1591
01:21:42.027 --> 01:21:44.863
But I think I'm done.

1592
01:21:46.406 --> 01:21:47.407
What are we gonna do?

1593
01:21:47.491 --> 01:21:49.201
We can't win without Jett.

1594
01:21:49.284 --> 01:21:51.870
What? We're all thinking it.

1595
01:22:02.631 --> 01:22:07.636
Look. "roots run deep".
that's more than just a cheer.

1596
01:22:08.637 --> 01:22:11.557
You guys have no idea
what you mean to this city.

1597
01:22:12.349 --> 01:22:15.561
My mom told me to dream big.

1598
01:22:16.144 --> 01:22:21.483
And for Vineland. there is no dream bigger
than bringing home a Claw.

1599
01:22:21.567 --> 01:22:24.486
This might be the last time
Vineland Thorns ever play.

1600
01:22:24.570 --> 01:22:26.363
And we ain't gonna go out like this.

1601
01:22:26.446 --> 01:22:28.574
Yeah. you heard the rook.

1602
01:22:30.409 --> 01:22:31.827
Let's dream big.

1603
01:22:41.503 --> 01:22:43.088
Is that-- Is that Jett?

1604
01:22:43.172 --> 01:22:45.215
-Did she just--
-Yeah. Jett!

1605
01:22:45.299 --> 01:22:48.302
-Jett. it's so good to see you again!
-Love you. Jett!

1606
01:22:50.721 --> 01:22:52.306
Jett. Jett.

1607
01:22:52.389 --> 01:22:55.976
Jett. Jett. Jett!

1608
01:22:56.059 --> 01:23:00.647
A well-deserved standing ovation
for the legendary Jett Fillmore.

1609
01:23:01.190 --> 01:23:02.608
Jett. Jett.

1610
01:23:02.691 --> 01:23:05.277
Jett. Jett. Jett.

1611
01:23:05.360 --> 01:23:06.612
Welcome back. GOAT.

1612
01:23:06.695 --> 01:23:09.781
Jett. Jett. Jett. Jett.

1613
01:23:11.366 --> 01:23:12.326
Archie.

1614
01:23:14.161 --> 01:23:15.913
Harris is on a tear.

1615
01:23:16.371 --> 01:23:17.998
The Thorns are all tied up.

1616
01:23:18.916 --> 01:23:20.959
-Olivia!
-I got this.

1617
01:23:29.676 --> 01:23:31.011
I am that bird.

1618
01:23:31.094 --> 01:23:32.596
I am that bird.

1619
01:23:38.060 --> 01:23:39.811
She can fly!

1620
01:23:39.895 --> 01:23:41.855
I can fly!

1621
01:23:41.939 --> 01:23:43.732
She can fly?

1622
01:23:45.275 --> 01:23:48.904
Olivia Burke just posterized Mane!

1623
01:23:48.987 --> 01:23:50.989
I am losing my mind here!

1624
01:23:51.073 --> 01:23:52.783
Olivia!

1625
01:23:52.866 --> 01:23:54.868
-That's right.
-Go. Livvy!

1626
01:23:54.952 --> 01:23:56.912
-Go. Thorns! Go. Thorns!
-We can do it!

1627
01:23:56.995 --> 01:23:59.373
Smalls ball! Ostriches fly!

1628
01:23:59.456 --> 01:24:01.458
These are the Thorns we came to see!

1629
01:24:01.542 --> 01:24:03.710
Look who's the poster child now.

1630
01:24:08.006 --> 01:24:09.800
Time out. Magma.

1631
01:24:09.883 --> 01:24:12.636
Word of advice? Stay off social media.

1632
01:24:13.178 --> 01:24:15.305
We gotta turn this around now.

1633
01:24:15.389 --> 01:24:19.351
-Where my Maniacs at?
-Mane! Mane! Mane!

1634
01:24:19.434 --> 01:24:22.312
Uh-oh. I think we've got
some seismic activity.

1635
01:24:22.396 --> 01:24:24.231
Just listen to that crowd.

1636
01:24:24.314 --> 01:24:28.026
-They're going crazy.
-Oh. yeah!

1637
01:24:28.569 --> 01:24:30.279
Let's go!

1638
01:24:34.157 --> 01:24:35.492
Archie's trapped with no way out.

1639
01:24:35.576 --> 01:24:36.869
I know the feeling. Rusty.

1640
01:24:37.703 --> 01:24:39.371
Whoa! And up goes Lenny.

1641
01:24:42.249 --> 01:24:44.459
Jett can't save you now.

1642
01:24:47.921 --> 01:24:49.214
Hard foul by Mane.

1643
01:24:49.298 --> 01:24:50.883
-What?
-You gotta call that!

1644
01:24:50.966 --> 01:24:53.343
The zebra and the horse
are working together.

1645
01:24:53.427 --> 01:24:55.012
-Boo!
-Come on! That's a foul.

1646
01:24:57.306 --> 01:24:59.433
Really? That's how you want to win?

1647
01:25:00.017 --> 01:25:02.144
What you gonna do about it. small?

1648
01:25:02.227 --> 01:25:03.478
Hey. Mane!

1649
01:25:04.188 --> 01:25:06.440
He's not a small.

1650
01:25:06.523 --> 01:25:11.361
He's a medium!

1651
01:25:11.445 --> 01:25:12.404
Hey. break it up!

1652
01:25:13.614 --> 01:25:16.700
-Let me at him! Let me at him!
-Relax!

1653
01:25:17.618 --> 01:25:20.495
Keep your hooves off my teammates.

1654
01:25:20.579 --> 01:25:21.747
Get him. Daddy!

1655
01:25:21.830 --> 01:25:23.540
Make him bleed!

1656
01:25:23.624 --> 01:25:25.125
That's not what you want to see.

1657
01:25:25.209 --> 01:25:26.543
Speak for yourself.

1658
01:25:26.627 --> 01:25:29.129
Flagrant two. Number 34. ejected.

1659
01:25:29.213 --> 01:25:31.465
Are you kidding me? Mane started it.

1660
01:25:31.548 --> 01:25:33.133
-Where's his foul?
-Cry about it.

1661
01:25:33.217 --> 01:25:36.136
The rules state
Thorns need five players or they forfeit.

1662
01:25:36.678 --> 01:25:37.804
Hit me again.

1663
01:25:39.890 --> 01:25:41.016
Okay. okay.

1664
01:25:41.099 --> 01:25:44.102
I haven't played since
my rec league days. but I guess I could--

1665
01:25:50.817 --> 01:25:52.069
Put me in. Coach.

1666
01:25:52.569 --> 01:25:55.155
I got a game to win.

1667
01:25:57.699 --> 01:25:59.326
Jett. you can barely walk.

1668
01:25:59.409 --> 01:26:02.579
No. We can't let you do this.
You'll just make it worse.

1669
01:26:02.663 --> 01:26:03.747
You think they bought it?

1670
01:26:05.082 --> 01:26:06.083
I do.

1671
01:26:06.166 --> 01:26:09.169
I think we have about three seconds
before they catch on.

1672
01:26:09.253 --> 01:26:11.046
But that's all we need. You all ready?

1673
01:26:11.129 --> 01:26:13.048
I've been trying to run a play
like this all season.

1674
01:26:13.131 --> 01:26:15.926
but some hothead kept interrupting me.

1675
01:26:16.009 --> 01:26:17.845
That's a great play.

1676
01:26:17.928 --> 01:26:19.847
Yeah. It was worth the wait.

1677
01:26:22.808 --> 01:26:23.976
Roots run deep!

1678
01:26:24.059 --> 01:26:26.520
The Thorns are down by two
with 20 seconds on the clock.

1679
01:26:26.603 --> 01:26:28.689
Jett's gonna lay it all on the line.

1680
01:26:28.772 --> 01:26:29.898
What a competitor!

1681
01:26:29.982 --> 01:26:31.650
Listen up. Double-team her.

1682
01:26:31.733 --> 01:26:33.527
Triple-team her if you have to.

1683
01:26:33.610 --> 01:26:35.904
Do not let her out of your sight.

1684
01:26:35.988 --> 01:26:37.322
Jett's fighting an injury.

1685
01:26:37.406 --> 01:26:38.574
The court is unstable.

1686
01:26:38.657 --> 01:26:40.993
Do you still want her
taking the final shot?

1687
01:26:41.076 --> 01:26:47.916
With fire and brimstone bringing judgment
and wrath to us all. I want Fillmore!

1688
01:27:29.208 --> 01:27:30.375
Will!

1689
01:27:32.878 --> 01:27:34.755
Come on. Get past me.

1690
01:27:34.838 --> 01:27:36.006
I don't have to.

1691
01:28:09.790 --> 01:28:12.417
Our bestie just won the Claw.

1692
01:28:12.501 --> 01:28:14.670
-That's my boy!
-Hold me. Daryl.

1693
01:28:15.712 --> 01:28:18.131
For the first time in 50 years.

1694
01:28:18.215 --> 01:28:20.092
the Vineland Thorns are champions!

1695
01:28:20.175 --> 01:28:22.052
Miracles can happen. folks.

1696
01:28:22.135 --> 01:28:23.762
I love this game.

1697
01:28:23.846 --> 01:28:26.306
And I love you. Rusty.

1698
01:28:27.641 --> 01:28:30.519
I love you too. Chuckles.

1699
01:28:37.401 --> 01:28:39.361
Attaboy. Will!

1700
01:28:39.444 --> 01:28:40.445
Honey!

1701
01:28:40.529 --> 01:28:43.031
Let's have another dozen kids.

1702
01:28:45.075 --> 01:28:49.788
Ten years. ten teams. one Claw. baby!

1703
01:28:49.872 --> 01:28:52.207
We are champions!

1704
01:28:52.291 --> 01:28:53.542
-Daddy!
-Daddy!

1705
01:28:53.625 --> 01:28:54.835
You were so cool.

1706
01:28:54.918 --> 01:28:57.671
Daddy was pretty cool. right?
I was like...

1707
01:28:58.964 --> 01:29:00.257
-We love you.
-We love you.

1708
01:29:01.341 --> 01:29:02.467
I love you girls.

1709
01:29:04.178 --> 01:29:07.347
Hey. Mane. Good game. Let me help you up.

1710
01:29:09.183 --> 01:29:12.728
-Hey. your hair is on fire.
-What?

1711
01:29:12.811 --> 01:29:14.521
Oh. no. No. No.

1712
01:29:14.605 --> 01:29:15.898
Not the hair.

1713
01:29:19.109 --> 01:29:20.819
-Will!
-Jett.

1714
01:29:20.903 --> 01:29:22.613
We're champions. baby.

1715
01:29:22.696 --> 01:29:25.032
Oh. Jett! We did it! We actually did it!

1716
01:29:25.115 --> 01:29:26.617
No. you did it.

1717
01:29:26.700 --> 01:29:28.410
Looks like moms was right.

1718
01:29:32.915 --> 01:29:33.957
-Jett. you okay?
-I'm fine.

1719
01:29:34.041 --> 01:29:35.042
-You good?
-I'm fine.

1720
01:29:35.125 --> 01:29:38.670
I just can't feel my legs.
but I'm a champion. baby.

1721
01:29:39.421 --> 01:29:43.300
Never thought I'd see the day
Jett Fillmore passed the ball.

1722
01:29:43.383 --> 01:29:44.384
Security!

1723
01:29:44.468 --> 01:29:45.677
Hold up. sucka.

1724
01:29:45.761 --> 01:29:49.056
-Playtime?
-Should we destroy?

1725
01:29:49.681 --> 01:29:51.517
Destroy!

1726
01:29:51.600 --> 01:29:54.061
Do you know who I am?

1727
01:29:54.144 --> 01:29:55.521
Hey. you were right about Will.

1728
01:29:55.604 --> 01:29:57.481
He's a great addition to the team.

1729
01:29:57.564 --> 01:29:59.191
Bye. piglet.

1730
01:29:59.733 --> 01:30:05.072
Introducing your Roar champions.

1731
01:30:05.155 --> 01:30:10.285
the Vineland Thorns!

1732
01:30:13.080 --> 01:30:16.166
Yeah! Let's go. Vineland! Let's go!

1733
01:30:18.085 --> 01:30:19.211
Horns up. everybody.

1734
01:30:19.294 --> 01:30:20.921
Vineland!

1735
01:30:21.755 --> 01:30:23.674
I think it's time they hear from...

1736
01:30:26.176 --> 01:30:27.261
the GOAT.

1737
01:30:27.886 --> 01:30:30.055
Will! Will! Will! Will!

1738
01:30:30.138 --> 01:30:31.890
Will! Will! Will!

1739
01:30:31.974 --> 01:30:33.392
Medium fries did it!

1740
01:30:38.021 --> 01:30:39.565
I... I...

1741
01:30:39.648 --> 01:30:41.483
I don't even know what to say right now.

1742
01:30:41.984 --> 01:30:43.902
-This is crazy.
-We love you. Will!

1743
01:30:43.986 --> 01:30:44.987
Oh. wow.

1744
01:30:46.446 --> 01:30:47.656
I mean.

1745
01:30:48.991 --> 01:30:51.034
I saw Jett play when...

1746
01:30:51.118 --> 01:30:52.369
when I was just a kid.

1747
01:30:53.203 --> 01:30:58.917
Then I told my mom. I said.
"I'm gonna be just like her."

1748
01:31:00.752 --> 01:31:02.462
And you know what's crazy?

1749
01:31:02.963 --> 01:31:05.507
My mom actually believed it.

1750
01:31:06.133 --> 01:31:09.469
She always seemed to know
those kinds of things. you know?

1751
01:31:09.553 --> 01:31:12.181
Like she always knew

1752
01:31:12.264 --> 01:31:15.350
that even if she couldn't be here for me.

1753
01:31:15.434 --> 01:31:17.644
Vineland would be.

1754
01:31:17.728 --> 01:31:19.688
You delivered for me...

1755
01:31:19.771 --> 01:31:21.440
Will done changed the game.

1756
01:31:22.065 --> 01:31:24.443
And you always had my back...

1757
01:31:26.195 --> 01:31:28.488
and you inspired me.

1758
01:31:30.866 --> 01:31:34.912
We brought the Claw home!

1759
01:31:40.125 --> 01:31:45.255
And even if the Thorns don't have
a home in Vineland anymore...

1760
01:31:48.425 --> 01:31:52.679
no one can take this Claw away from us!

1761
01:31:55.766 --> 01:31:58.977
Vineland will be champions forever!

1762
01:32:00.979 --> 01:32:03.357
Modo has something to say!

1763
01:32:04.274 --> 01:32:08.904
Thorns staying in Vineland!

1764
01:32:10.322 --> 01:32:13.325
Modo is team owner.

1765
01:32:13.408 --> 01:32:14.660
Wait. How?

1766
01:32:19.748 --> 01:32:20.999
All in.

1767
01:32:21.083 --> 01:32:22.376
All in.

